description: SpectrumSharingFunction:  Records details of spectrum sharing functions, including timestamp, location, cell ID, and function identifiers.  `dateTime`: Timestamp of record; `Area_Name`: Geographic area of the cell; `CellId`: Unique identifier for the cell; `Id2`:  (Likely a redundant cell ID); `Id3`:  (Likely an internal sequential ID); `vsDataType`: Data type identifier; `vsDataFormatVersion`: Version of the data format; `SpectrumSharingFunction.spectrumSharingFunctionId`: Unique ID of the spectrum sharing function.
